C-ODEPACK is a wrapper interface for ODEPACK. 

ODEPACK is a general Differential equation integrator written by Alan C. Hindmarsh and others at LLNL. It can be obtained from netlib or from here:
https://computation.llnl.gov/casc/odepack/odepack_home.html
See ODEPACK documentation for information about citing ODEPACK.

